omb\nlattice suggests an experimental procedure to search for honeycomb topological\nmagnon insulators within a class of 2D quantum magnets and ultracold atoms\ntrapped in honeycomb optical lattices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Feb 2016 13:46:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Feb 2016 16:35:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 25 Feb 2016 14:56:35 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 11 May 2016 16:15:53 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2016 19:10:46 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2016 15:52:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-21"}
