 inhomogeneous isocurvature field fluctuation might give rise to\nsome of the observed anomalies. In particular, we focus on the Cold Spot, the\npower deficit at low multipoles and the breaking of statistical isotropy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Feb 2016 15:11:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2016 13:20:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-04"}
